response.overview: This band from Ft. Wayne, Alabama - Randy Owen, Teddy Gentry, Jeff Cook, and Mark Herndon - has become an unprecedented supergroup. With 18 consecutive #1 country singles, the group holds an all-time record of chart success.  All the videos in this collection are #1 hits.  From the sultry "Fire in the NIght" to the classic "Mountain Music" = plus seven others - the group captures a spirit of good times and good music.
response.title: Alabama: Greatest Video Hits
